				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Text to Text | President Johnson&#8217;s &#8216;Great Society&#8217; Speech and &lsquo;50 Years Into the War on Poverty, Hardship Hits Back&#8217;</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Michael Gonchar			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-05-06T20:52:40+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">May 6, 2014 4:52 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">May 6, 2014 4:52 pm</span>		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content"><div class="w592"><figure class="media photo promo" itemprop="associatedMedia" itemscope="" itemid="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/04/21/us/Appalachia-LN/Appalachia-tmagArticle.jpg" itemtype="//schema.org/ImageObject" role="group"><span class="visually-hidden">Photo</span><div class="image"><img itemprop="url" itemid="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/04/21/us/Appalachia-LN/Appalachia-tmagArticle.jpg" src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/04/21/us/Appalachia-LN/Appalachia-tmagArticle.jpg" id="100000002865097" width="592" height="395" alt="Emalee Short played with her dog outside her grandparentsâ home in Hensley, W.Va., in long-struggling McDowell County. &lt;a href=&quot;//www.nytimes.com/2014/04/21/us/50-years-into-the-war-on-poverty-hardship-hits-back.html&quot;&gt;Related Article&lt;/a&gt;"   /><meta itemprop="height" content="395"><meta itemprop="width" content="592"></div><figcaption class="caption" itemprop="description"><span class="caption-text">Emalee Short played with her dog outside her grandparentsâ home in Hensley, W.Va., in long-struggling McDowell County. <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/04/21/us/50-years-into-the-war-on-poverty-hardship-hits-back.html">Related Article</a></span><span class="credit" itemprop="copyrightHolder"><span class="visually-hidden">Credit</span> Travis Dove for The New York Times</span></figcaption></figure></div>
<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//learning.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/05/06/text-to-text-president-johnsons-great-society-speech-and-50-years-into-the-war-on-poverty-hardship-hits-back/" data-title="Text to Text | President Johnson&#8217;s &#8216;Great Society&#8217; Speech and &lsquo;50 Years Into the War on Poverty, Hardship Hits Back&#8217;" data-description="In this Text to Text, we pair President Johnson&#039;s &quot;Great Society&quot; speech with an article by Trip Gabriel describing the new face of poverty in rural West Virginia. ">
